fields.description_of_change:
Based on DCP-VTX-22-003. 
Change is made to add a mounting point for the engine control system (ECS):
1. Change the applicability of DD - 913A1001-002 (see appendix 1);
2. Add new DD - 913A1001-012.
fields.solutions: The changes are described in Attachment 1.

fields.description_of_change:
CA781A0000-004 (TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS FOR EXHAUST NOZZLE INSTALLATION)
1. Delete:
CLN000003 | ABRASIVE SURFACE CLEANING PER VRT-PS-223.
Cleaning surfaces 03-18
2. Add:
Cleaning surfaces for the contact areas between parts: 781A0000-201 – 781A0000-203, 781A0000-203 - 781A4000-004, 
781A0000-200 - 781A0000-202, 781A0000-202 - 781A4000-004.
For the edges of areas of contact between parts: 781A0000-201 – 781A0000-203, 781A0000-203 - 781A4000-004, 
781A0000-200 - 781A0000-202, 781A0000-202 - 781A4000-004 add fillet seal:
